拉美最大的VTuber经纪公司之一OWOZU“所有人才都会离开”的消息是否正在传播？ https://p2y.jp/latin-america-largest-vtuber-agency-owozu-all-talents-left/ https://p2y.jp/latin-america-largest-vtuber-agency-owozu-all-talents-left/#respondp2y_admin Tue, 30 Jan 2024 04:50:00 +0000 VTuberバーチャルOWOZUredditTwitterYouTuberスペイン語セクハラバーチャルYouTuber中米南米 https://p2y.jp/?p=113263 <p>近日，有未经证实的消息传出，拉丁美洲VTuber经纪公司OWOZU旗下艺人已全部离开该公司。该信息的真实性尚未得到证实 […]</p><a href="https://p2y.jp/latin-america-largest-vtuber-agency-owozu-all-talents-left/">中南美洲最大的VTuber经纪公司之一OWOZU“所有人才将离开”的消息正在传播？</a>首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a> .; <p></p><p>近日，拉美VTuber经纪公司<strong>OWOZU</strong>经证实，有未经证实的消息称其艺人已全部离开该机构。</p><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><strong>该信息包括真实性尚未确认的信息。一旦事实得到证实，我们将立即更新这篇文章。</strong> </p></blockquote><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" data-attachment-id="88928" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/latin-american-vtuber-agency-owozu-has-risen-to-2nd-place-in-the-world-in-average-number-of-youtube-subscribers-per-talents/latin_american_vtuber_agency_owozu_has_risen_to_2nd_place_in_the_world_in_average_number_of_youtube_subscribers_per_talents/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/latin_american_vtuber_agency_owozu_has_risen_to_2nd_place_in_the_world_in_average_number_of_youtube_subscribers_per_talents.jpg" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="latin_american_vtuber_agency_owozu_has_risen_to_2nd_place_in_the_world_in_average_number_of_youtube_subscribers_per_talents" data-image-description="" data